        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nGreat work, Dan!  I will bring up that several projects in ODL are attempting to move away from jackson in favor of gson for serialization.  We have ~3-4 serialization libraries right now and are working to consolidate on gson.  However, there is a lot of technical debt in ripping some of them out!",
